quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,alrhmn ellam al'iinsan alqran; btysyr tilawatih whfzh wafahm meanyh
  55,2,alrhmn ellam al'iinsan alqran; btysyr tilawatih whfzh wafahm meanyh
  55,3,"khlq al'insan, ellamh albayan emma fi nafsih tmyyzana lah ean ghyrh"
  55,4,"khlq al'insan, ellamh albayan emma fi nafsih tmyyzana lah ean ghyrh"
  55,5,"alshms walqamar yjryan mteaqbayn bhsab mtqn, la yakhtalif wala ydtrb"
  55,6,"walnjm aladhi fi alsama' wa'ashjar alard, taerif rabiha wtsjd lh, wtnqad lamaa skhrraha lah min masalih eibadih wmnafehm"
  55,7,"walsma' rafaeaha fawq alard, wawade fi al'ard aleadl aldhy 'amr bih wshreh lebadh"
  55,8,"lyla taetaduu watakhunuu man wazantm lh, wa'aqimuu alwazn baledl, wala tunqisu almizan 'iidha wazantm llnas"
  55,9,"lyla taetaduu watakhunuu man wazantm lh, wa'aqimuu alwazn baledl, wala tunqisu almizan 'iidha wazantm llnas"
  55,10,"walard wadeiha wmhhadha; lystqr ealayha alkhlq. fiha fakihat alnakhl dhat alaweyt alty yakun minha althmr, wafiha alhabi dhu alqshr; rzqana lakum wlaneamkm, wafiha kl nbt tayib alrayht"
  55,11,"walard wadeiha wmhhadha; lystqr ealayha alkhlq. fiha fakihat alnakhl dhat alaweyt alty yakun minha althmr, wafiha alhabi dhu alqshr; rzqana lakum wlaneamkm, wafiha kl nbt tayib alrayht"
  55,12,"walard wadeiha wmhhadha; lystqr ealayha alkhlq. fiha fakihat alnakhl dhat alaweyt alty yakun minha althmr, wafiha alhabi dhu alqshr; rzqana lakum wlaneamkm, wafiha kl nbt tayib alrayht"
  55,13,"fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma aldiyniat waldnywyt- ya maeshar aljini wal'ins- tkdhdhiban? wama 'ahsan jawab aljini hin tala ealayhim alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wasalam hadhih alswrt, fklma mara bhdhh alayt, qalu: \"wla bishay' min alayk rbbana nkdhb, falak alhmd\", whkdha yanbaghi lileabd 'iidha tuliat ealayh nem allah walawh, 'an yuqrr bha, wyshkr allah wyhmdh elyha"
  55,14,"khlq 'aba al'insan, wahu adam min tin yabis kalfakhkhar, wakhalaq 'iblys, wahu min aljini man lahab alnaar almukhtalit baedah bbed"
  55,15,"khlq 'aba al'insan, wahu adam min tin yabis kalfakhkhar, wakhalaq 'iblys, wahu min aljini man lahab alnaar almukhtalit baedah bbed"
  55,16,fbay nieam rbkma- ya maeshar al'iins waljn- tkdhdhiban?
  55,17,"hw subhanah wteala rbb mshrqay alshams fi alshita' walsyf, warabu mghrbayha fyhma, faljmye taht tdbyrh wrbwbyth"
  55,18,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,19,"khlt allah ma'an albahrayn - aledhb walmlh- yltqyan. baynahuma hajz, fala yatghaa 'ahaduhuma ealaa alakhr, wayudhhib bkhsaysh, bal yabqaa aledhb edhbana, walmlh mlhana mae tlaqyhma"
  55,20,"khlt allah ma'an albahrayn - aledhb walmlh- yltqyan. baynahuma hajz, fala yatghaa 'ahaduhuma ealaa alakhr, wayudhhib bkhsaysh, bal yabqaa aledhb edhbana, walmlh mlhana mae tlaqyhma"
  55,21,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,22,ykhrj min albahrayn bqdrt allah alluwlu walmarjan
  55,23,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,24,"wlh subhanah wteala alsufun aldakhmat alty tajri fi albahr bmnafe alnas, raafieat qlaeha washretha kaljbal"
  55,25,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,26,"kl man ealaa wajh al'ard min alkhalq halk, wybqa wajh rabik dhu alezmt walkbrya' walfadl waljwd. wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat alwajh lilah taealaa bima ylyq bih sbhanh, dun tshbyh wala tkyyf"
  55,27,"kl man ealaa wajh al'ard min alkhalq halk, wybqa wajh rabik dhu alezmt walkbrya' walfadl waljwd. wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat alwajh lilah taealaa bima ylyq bih sbhanh, dun tshbyh wala tkyyf"
  55,28,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,29,"ysalh man fi alsmwat wal'ard hajathm, fala ghinaan li'ahad minhum eanh sbhanh. kula yawm hu fi shan: yueizz wyudhillu, wyety wyamne"
  55,30,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,31,"snfrugh lhsabkm wmjazatkm baemalkma alty emltmwhma fi aldnya, 'ayuha althqlan- al'iins waljn-, fneaqb 'ahl almeasy, wnuthyb 'ahl altaet"
  55,32,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,33,"ya maeshar aljini wal'ins, 'iina qadartm ealaa alnafadh min 'amr allah whkmh harbyn min 'atraf alsmwat wal'ard fafelu, walastum qadirin ealaa dhlk 'iilaa biquat whjt, wamur min allah taealaa (wanna lakum dhlk wa'antum la tamlikun li'anfusikum nfeana wala drana?). fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma - 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,34,"ya maeshar aljini wal'ins, 'iina qadartm ealaa alnafadh min 'amr allah whkmh harbyn min 'atraf alsmwat wal'ard fafelu, walastum qadirin ealaa dhlk 'iilaa biquat whjt, wamur min allah taealaa (wanna lakum dhlk wa'antum la tamlikun li'anfusikum nfeana wala drana?). fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma - 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,35,"yursal ealaykum lahab min nar, wanuhas mdhab yusabb ealaa rwwskm, fala yansur baedukum bedana ya maeshar aljini wal'ins. fabi'ayi nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,36,"yursal ealaykum lahab min nar, wanuhas mdhab yusabb ealaa rwwskm, fala yansur baedukum bedana ya maeshar aljini wal'ins. fabi'ayi nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,37,"f'idha anshaqat alsama' wtftrt yawm alqyamt, fakanat hamra' klwn alwrd, wkalzyt almghly walrasas almdhab; min shdt al'amr whwl yawm alqyamt"
  55,38,fbay nieam rbkma- 'ayuha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,39,fafi dhlk alyawm la tus'al almalayikat almujrimin min al'iins waljini ean dhnwbhm
  55,40,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,41,"taerif almalayikat almujrimin belamathm, ftakhdhhm bmqdmt rwwshm wbaqdamhm, ftrmyhm fi alnar"
  55,42,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,43,"yqal lhwla' almujrimin -twbykhana wthqyrana lhm-: hadhih jahanam alati ykdhdhib biha almujrimun fi aldnya: taratan yuedhdhabwn fi aljhym, wtart yusqwn min alhmym, wahu sharab balagh mntha alhrart, yqttie alamea' walahsha'"
  55,44,"yqal lhwla' almujrimin -twbykhana wthqyrana lhm-: hadhih jahanam alati ykdhdhib biha almujrimun fi aldnya: taratan yuedhdhabwn fi aljhym, wtart yusqwn min alhmym, wahu sharab balagh mntha alhrart, yqttie alamea' walahsha'"
  55,45,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,46,"wlmn atqa allah min eibadih min al'iins waljn, fkhaf mqamh bayn ydyh, fataeh, wtrk measyh, jntan"
  55,47,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,48,aljntan dhawata aghsan nadratan min alfwakh walthmar
  55,49,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,50,fy hatayn aljanatayn eaynan min alma' tajrian khlalhma
  55,51,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,52,fy hatayn aljanatayn min kuli nawe min alfwakh snfan
  55,53,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,54,"wlldhyn khafuu maqam rabihim janatan ytnemwn fyhma, mutakiiyn ealaa furush mbttant min ghaliz aldybaj, wthmr aljanatayn qarib 'ilyhm"
  55,55,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,56,"fy hadhih alfrsh zwjat qasirat 'absarihina ealaa azwajhn, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyrhm mtelqat bhm, lm ytahn 'iins qablahum wala jan"
  55,57,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,58,kan hwla' alzwjat min alhwr alyaqwt walmarjan fi sfayhn wjmalhn
  55,59,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,60,hal jaza' man 'ahsan bemlh fi aldunya 'iilaa al'iihsan 'iilayh bialjanat fi alakhr? fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,61,hl jaza' man 'ahsan bemlh fi aldunya 'iilaa al'iihsan 'iilayh bialjanat fi alakhr? fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,62,wmn dun aljanatayn alssabiqatayn janatan akhryan. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,63,wmn dun aljanatayn alssabiqatayn janatan akhryan. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,64,"hatan aljntan khdrawan, qad ashtddat khdrthma hataa malt 'iilaa alswad. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,65,"hatan aljntan khdrawan, qad ashtddat khdrthma hataa malt 'iilaa alswad. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,66,fyhma eaynan fwwartan bialma' la tnqtean. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,67,fyhma eaynan fwwartan bialma' la tnqtean. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,68,fy hatayn aljanatayn 'anwae alfwakh wanakhl wrman
  55,69,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,70,fy hadhih aljnan al'arbae zwjat tayibat al'akhlaq hisan alwjwh
  55,71,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,72,hwr mstwrat mswnat fi alkhyam
  55,73,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,74,lm yta hwla' alhwr 'iins qabl 'azwajahuna wala jan
  55,75,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,76,mtkyyn ealaa wsayd dhwat aghtyt khadir wafurush hsan
  55,77,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,78,"tkathrt brkt asm rabik wkthr khyrh, dhi aljalal albahr, walmjd alkaml, wal'iikram lawlyayh"